"3/4 cup kosher salt (if using Morton) or 1 cup (if using Jacobsen or Diamond Crystal)*","1 teaspoon peppercorns","1  turkey (12 to 14 lbs.), butterflied*","3  to 4 tbsp. olive oil","1 teaspoon ground pepper","  Herb sprigs, such as sage, rosemary, thyme, and/or parsley"